Recommends: flatpak
Description: Linux System Optimizer and Monitor (GNUTUX)
 GT-STACER is a modern fork of Stacer, rebuilt with Qt6 and C++17 for
 GNU/Linux 2026 by the GNUTUX project.
 .
 Features: real-time system monitoring (CPU, GPU, memory, disk, network,
 temperature, battery), process manager, systemd service manager, startup
 applications, system cleaner, package manager (APT+Flatpak+Snap),
 APT repository manager, and a /etc/hosts editor.
 .
